What is nodeJs

Backend framework of javascript
Help to build api

Single Thread, non blocking , async I/O 

NPM > node package manager

>>>>>>>>>>>>>><<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<
package.json
> entry point to application
> name of application
> version of application
> description
> author
> lisence 
> scripts(start,stop,build,test)
> packages/dependency 

/////////////////////
Step to generate package.json
/////////////////////
**NodeJs must be installed in system
> navigate to folder where you want to generate using cmd /terminal
> npm init
> answer all question
> type "yes"

>>>>>>>>>>>>>><<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<
local dependency >  for application development
dev dependency > user for time of testing
global dependency > use to create application & run


/////////////////////
Step to install local dependency
///////////////////
** NodeJs must be install in system
> got inside folder where you want to install
> npm i packagename

/////////////////////
Step to install dev dependency
///////////////////
** nodeJs must be install in system
> got inside folder where you want to install
> npm i packagename --save-dev

/////////////////////
Step to install global dependency
///////////////////
#window
> open cmd as admin
> npm i -g packagename

#linux
> open terminal
> sudo npm i -g packagename

> any dependency added will not added in package.json
> it need admin permission
> it install in system directly 
